OL,6,FA "deplorable" nurse who illegally
OL,7,Fdrugged patients on a hospital stroke
OL,8,Funit for an "easy life" has been
OL,9,Fstruck off the nursing register.
OL,11,FCatherine Hudson, 54, was jailed for
OL,12,Fseven years and two months in December
OL,13,F2023 for illegally sedating two
OL,14,Fpatients at Blackpool Victoria
OL,15,FHospital and conspiring with colleague
OL,16,FCharlotte Wilmot, 48, to sedate a
OL,17,Fthird.
