OL,3,CNurse struck off register for
OL,4,Cillegally drugging patients
OL,6,FMore than a year after being
OL,7,Fconviction Hudson has now been struck
OL,8,Foff by the Nursing and Midwifery
OL,9,FCouncil (NMC) following a hearing.
OL,11,FIn November 2018, police were alerted
OL,12,Fby hospital staff after a student
OL,13,Fnurse reported that Hudson had
OL,14,Fsuggested giving an unprescribed
OL,15,Fsleeping pill to an elderly patient.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
