OL,3,CNurse struck off register for
OL,4,Cillegally drugging patients
OL,6,FAfter a hearing on 6 January, Hudson
OL,7,Fwas struck off by the NMC, with a
OL,8,Freport stating that her conduct "put
OL,9,Fvulnerable patients at risk of
OL,10,Fsignificant harm", and highlighted her
OL,11,Fcontempt for her patients.
OL,13,FShe gave one victim, 76-year-old
OL,14,FAileen Scott - who had been paralysed
OL,15,Fby a stroke - an unprescribed
OL,16,Fsedative, zopiclone, to keep her
OL,17,F"quiet and compliant".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
