OL,4,Cillegally drugging patients
OL,6,FMs Scott had travelled from Glasgow to
OL,7,FBlackpool with her son in October 2018
OL,8,Fwhen she suffered a stroke and was
OL,9,Frushed to hospital.
OL,11,FHer son described the pair as "pure
OL,12,Fevil" and said his mum's treatment
OL,13,Fwould "haunt" her family for the rest
OL,14,Fof their lives.
OL,16,FShe wrote about one of her victims in
OL,17,Fa WhatsApp message: "I sedated one of
OL,18,Fthem to within an inch of her life
OL,19,Flol. Bet she's flat for a week haha
OL,20,Fxxx."
