OL,4,Cillegally drugging patients
OL,6,FThe NMC panel noted remarks made by
OL,7,Fthe judge at Hudson's sentencing in
OL,8,F2023, where the judge stated that:
OL,9,F"The patients were as vulnerable as
OL,10,Fanyone could be. They could not leave
OL,11,Fthe stroke unit.
OL,13,F"Some of them found it difficult to
OL,14,Fmake themselves understood. These
OL,15,Fdefendants exploited them for an easy
OL,16,Fshift, for amusement, to exercise a
OL,17,Fcontemptuous power over them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
