OL,3,CNurse struck off register for
OL,4,Cillegally drugging patients
OL,6,FThe panel found Hudson's conduct of
OL,7,Fdeliberate ill-treatment of multiple
OL,8,Fvulnerable patients, stealing drugs
OL,9,Fand deliberately attempting to destroy
OL,10,Fevidence, together with her contempt
OL,11,Fand disregard towards patients and
OL,12,Ftheir families was indicative of
OL,13,Fdangerous and deep-seated attitudinal
OL,14,Fissues.
OL,16,FThe panel noted that concerns of
OL,17,Fdishonesty and attitudinal issues are
OL,18,Fdifficult to remediate, and determined
OL,19,Fthat there was a "high risk" of
OL,20,FHudson's behaviour being repeated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
