OL,6,FA report from the misconduct hearing
OL,7,Fsaid: "Mrs Hudson's actions were
OL,8,Fsignificant departures from the
OL,9,Fstandards expected of a registered
OL,10,Fnurse and in the panel's judgement
OL,11,Fthey were fundamentally incompatible
OL,12,Fwith her remaining on the register.
OL,14,FThe panel was of the view that a
OL,15,Fmember of the public would find it
OL,16,Fmorally reprehensible if a nurse were
OL,17,Fallowed to practise having been
OL,18,Fconvicted of ill-treatment of
OL,19,Fpatients, theft of drugs and
OL,20,Fperverting the course of justice."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
