OL,4,Cillegally drugging patients
OL,6,FWhile the striking-off order cannot
OL,7,Ftake effect until the end of a 28-day
OL,8,Fappeal period, the panel has also
OL,9,Fimposed an interim suspension order
OL,10,Ffor 18 months to cover any potential
OL,11,Fappeal period.
OL,13,FBand five staff nurse Hudson, 54, was
OL,14,Fsentenced at Preston Crown Court for
OL,15,Fthree offences of ill-treatment and
OL,16,Fone of conspiracy to ill-treat in
OL,17,Frelation to vulnerable patients at
OL,18,FBlackpool Victoria Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
