OL,3,CNurse struck off register for
OL,4,Cillegally drugging patients
OL,6,FShe was also sentenced for conspiring
OL,7,Fto steal five different medications
OL,8,Ffrom the hospital and perverting the
OL,9,Fcourse of justice by attempting to
OL,10,Fdispose of the medication.
OL,12,FHudson, of Blackpool, pleaded guilty
OL,13,Fto theft of Omeprazole, conspiracy to
OL,14,Fsteal Omeprazole, conspiracy to steal
OL,15,FAmoxicillin x2, conspiracy to steal
OL,16,FZopiclone x2, perverting the course of
OL,17,Fjustice, conspiracy to steal
OL,18,FTrimethoprim, conspiracy to steal
OL,19,FMetronidazole.
